{"tid":1698433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推上熱門】點解依日行程冇人推㗎？？","createTime":"2019-11-07T13:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:40:35.000Z","uid":60855,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"21c146a12278176ae86ad4a56cfcdbd645e50307","tid":1698433,"uid":60855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"11.12國父誕辰快閃‼️<br />\nDr. Sun Yat-sen&rsquo;s Birthday Flash Mob<br />\n<br />\n1112 沙田快閃紀念  <br />\n12Nov  New town Plaza, Sha Tin<br />\n<br />\n國父 孫中山同香港關係極深，佢嘅革命思想嚟自香港。百幾年前依位暴徒之父就係喺香港策劃咗好多次顏色革命，最終推翻咗滿清政權。<br />\n<br />\n國父為民主自由奮鬥咗一世人，佢嘅精神今日仍然激勵住爭取民主自由嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n九七前英國設一日假期俾我地緬懷依位 中山先生，但係嗰個尊稱 國父為「革命先行者」嘅共產匪黨喺「回归」後反而取消咗。<br />\n<br />\n所以喺今年暴政鎮壓之際，等我地一齊去紀念暴徒之父誕辰嘅日子，並且認識 國父與香港抗爭嘅關係，以及勉勵港人反抗到底。<br />\n<br />\n時代革命尚未成功<br />\n光復香港仍須努力<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情：<br />\n<br />\n日期：11月12日（二）<br />\n時間：20:00<br />\n地點：沙田新城市廣場中庭<br />\n<br />\n活動內容：<br />\n短講：國父與香港抗爭的關係<br />\n和你唱 （會唱 國父紀念歌～）"},{"pid":"c0f44ef6ddefbb4eae733aa9bc95ae88bb11b0ab","tid":1698433,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d6326bab9c4e36667049dcccdd2793fb9ce4c73","tid":1698433,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc9c4e526468108a2e3ece0ce6562f47775df28","tid":1698433,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2957808eb871a03fd91c078112f3a1f6e8c84a6","tid":1698433,"uid":60855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:08:40.000Z"